    "required_age": "12",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《吾家有女 Ai》是一款古风修仙题材多结局模拟养成游戏。您在游戏中将扮演一位受凤凰托付抚育其幼子逐渐长大的的父亲/母亲，您需要在这个过程中看护照料您的女儿，帮助她完成修成仙法，飞升仙界的梦想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/7fd7cada1d29812b63df97cd56cd6553.avif?t=1765836012\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与女儿自由对话</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在八年的游戏时间中，您可以自由地与您的女儿对话； 也可以通过文字指令，规划她的生活日常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/289a60de28ba868de268f30f4597053d.poster.avif?t=1765836012\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/289a60de28ba868de268f30f4597053d.webm?t=1765836012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/289a60de28ba868de268f30f4597053d.mp4?t=1765836012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日常修行与探索</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在您的安排下，您的女儿会在宗门长老的指引下修习仙法；也需要在宗门下属的各种产业中打工，以缴纳修习需要的灵石；合理地为她安排休息时间，避免她过度劳累病倒在床；除此之外安排她去野外进行探索，击败怪物，获得种种道具资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/45219c5b20a4bddb41a44cc4898bada3.poster.avif?t=1765836012\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/45219c5b20a4bddb41a44cc4898bada3.webm?t=1765836012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/45219c5b20a4bddb41a44cc4898bada3.mp4?t=1765836012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>正确的引导与目标改变</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成长中的少女，她的目标也很容易受到外界的影响，时时刻刻都有可能发生改变。并会按照新的目标，安排规划自己的活动行程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/6bacf03fe5b672416f24c64a74f31cc3.poster.avif?t=1765836012\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/6bacf03fe5b672416f24c64a74f31cc3.webm?t=1765836012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/6bacf03fe5b672416f24c64a74f31cc3.mp4?t=1765836012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不同人生所达成的多种结局</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >养育方式不同，您的女儿最终能达成的结局也大不相同。去探索收集它们吧！看看您与您的女儿将会走向怎样的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/bc0d3cfe61ac63ff3eb08c6797b90962.poster.avif?t=1765836012\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/bc0d3cfe61ac63ff3eb08c6797b90962.webm?t=1765836012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227670/extras/bc0d3cfe61ac63ff3eb08c6797b90962.mp4?t=1765836012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
